gololang.ir

Class TryCatchFinally

  • java.lang.Object
    • gololang.ir.GoloElement<T>
      • gololang.ir.GoloStatement<TryCatchFinally>
        • gololang.ir.TryCatchFinally

  • public final class TryCatchFinally
extends GoloStatement<TryCatchFinally>
    A try catch finally statement.

    Represents nodes such as: 

    
 try {
   # try block
 } catch (ex) {
   # catch block
 } finally {
   # finally block
 }
